# 🎬 Entertainment News Bot — @anime_24hr

A fully automated Telegram channel bot that posts movies, anime, K-drama, Indian cinema, web series, breaking news and trailer drops — every 30 minutes.

## Features
- 🎬 Movies, Anime, K-Drama, Indian (ML/TA/HI/TE), Web Series from TMDB & Jikan
- 📰 Breaking news via Google News RSS (box office, trailers, announcements)
- 🎬 Smart trailer detector — posts when a new trailer drops on TMDB
- 📋 Daily digest at 9 PM
- 🍿 Weekend watchlist every Friday
- 🔔 DM alert if bot has nothing to post for 2.5 hours
- 🚫 Content quality filter + duplicate prevention

## Setup

### 1. Clone the repo
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/entertainment-bot.git
cd entertainment-bot
```

### 2. Install dependencies
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 3. Create your .env file
```bash
cp .env.example .env
# Fill in your API keys
```

### 4. Run
```bash
python bot.py
```

## API Keys (all free)

| Key | Where |
|-----|-------|
| TMDB_API_KEY | themoviedb.org → Settings → API |
| TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN | @BotFather on Telegram |
| TELEGRAM_CHANNEL_ID | Your channel ID |
| GROQ_API_KEY | console.groq.com |
| OMDB_API_KEY | omdbapi.com |
| ADMIN_CHAT_ID | Your Telegram user ID |
| CHANNEL_WATERMARK | e.g. @anime_24hr |

## Schedule

| Task | Frequency |
|------|-----------|
| Content posts | Every 30 mins |
| Breaking news | Every 30 mins |
| Trailer detector | Every 2 hours |
| Daily digest | 9 PM daily |
| Weekend watchlist | Friday 6 PM |